ts or comments.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Entire Agreement</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">The above Terms of Service constitute the entire agreement of the parties and supersede any and all preceding and contemporaneous agreements between you and www.khatishodai.com . Any waiver of any provision of the Terms of Service will be effective only if in writing and signed by a Director of www.khatishodai.com</span></p><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</span></h1>', '<p class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Privacy Policy</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">This Privacy Policy manages the manner in which Khati Shodai collects, uses, maintains and discloses information collected from users of the www.khatishodai.com website. This privacy policy is applicable for the Site with all products and services offered by Khati Shodai.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">Personal&nbsp;Information</strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">Information customers give us:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">We may collect personal identification information from users in different ways, like, when users visit our site, register on the site, place an order, fill out a form, respond to a survey, subscribe to the newsletter and in connection with other activities, services, features or resources we have on our site.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">What kind of information:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">Users may be asked for, name, email address, billing address, shipping address, phone number, debit/credit card information etc. when required. Whenever the users interact with our website we get information like their browser names, device type, the means of connection with our site, their internet connection details, their location, and other similar information.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">Automatic Information (Cookies):</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">We receive and store certain types of information whenever the user interacts with us. For example, like many web sites, we use \"cookies,\" to enhance user experience. The user may choose to set their web browser to refuse cookies or to alert them when cookies are being sent. If they do so, note that some parts of the site may not function properly.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">Bulk SMS/Masking SMS:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">If you ever placed any order via the website or use our Meena Click Shopping app, we may send you promotional and transactional bulk SMS/Masking SMS. This promotional or transaction will notify you regarding upcoming or current offers and transactional updates. (OTP, Order confirmation, order delivered etc.)</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">E-mail Communications:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">We get the user\'s email addresses when they place an order through our website. We send our newsletter and different offers according to the customer profile to them. If the user does not want to receive e-mail or other promotional offers from us, they can unsubscribe easily by calling our Customer Support on </span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">01304327225</span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">. (24/7 every day)</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">Payment:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">If you have already made a payment twice for your single purchase, then please contact your bank to reverse the payment or cancel the payment as in Khati Shodai we have no control or access to your payments. Your payment related information is also kept secret to us from the bank. During the payment process, if you get disconnected then please contact your bank to ensure if the payment went through or not, if not then please make the payment again.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">How Do We Use This Information?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">Khati Shodai collects and uses Users personal information for the following purposes:</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">To improve customer service:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">Your information helps us to more effectively respond to your customer service requests and support needs.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">To improve our Site:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">We continually strive to improve our website offerings based on the information and feedback we receive from you.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">To process transactions:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">We may use the information users provide only to respond to their product requests. We do not share this information with anyone else except to the extent necessary to provide the service. We may provide your name and address to a third party in order to make delivery of the product to you (for example to our courier or supplier). You must only submit to us the Site information which is accurate and not misleading and you must keep it up to date and inform us of changes.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">To send periodic emails:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">The email address Users provide us for order processing, will only be used to send them information and updates related to their order. It may also be used to respond to their inquiries, and/or other requests or questions. If User decides to opt-in to our mailing list, they will receive emails that may include company news, updates, related product or service information, etc. If at any time the User would like to unsubscribe from receiving future emails, we include detailed unsubscribe instructions at the bottom of each email or User may contact us via our Site. User can also request to unsubscribe easily by calling our Customer Support on </span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">01304327225 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">(24/7 every day)</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">How do we protect your information?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">We adopt appropriate data collection, storage, and processing practices and security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure or destruction of your personal information, username, password, transaction information and data stored on our Site. When we collect data through the Site, we collect your personal details on a secure server. Our security procedures mean that we may occasionally request proof of identity before we disclose personal information to you. You are responsible for protecting against unauthorized access to your password and to your computer. we shall not sell or disclose your personal data to third parties without obtaining your prior consent unless this is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy or unless we are required to do so by law.</span></p>', '<h1><strong style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67);\">About Khati shodai</strong></h1><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">Khatishodai.com is one of the fast growing online e-commerce stores in&nbsp;Dhaka, Bangladesh which is resolved to convey best quality items to the people, families just as the corporate clients in the simplest manner.</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 94, 88); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"> We guarantee the best quality and quickest home conveyance administration With an assorted scope of items like Organic, Grocery, Clothing &amp; Fashion, Beauty, Home Decoration, Baby Care, stationery, Electronic items and so on We also committed within two hour home delivery service with accepting&nbsp;COD (cash on delivery), bkash, nagad, rocket, debit/credit card payment facilities.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(97, 94, 88);\">Khatishodai strives to utilize the power of the internet in its highest peak to fulfil the needs of your busy life.Corporate and exceptional clients are profoundly invited to appreciate unique proposals from us.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">&nbsp;</span></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67);\">Message From CEO</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Khati Shodai is owned by MD Noor Iqbal&nbsp;. He is the first generation&nbsp;owner of this company. This company used to be a local retailer of grocery products in Mohammadpur. Seeing the growth of online shopping MD Noor Iqbal decided to completely move towards an online-based platform. There are a lot of people who are tricking customers into buying fake, unauthentic products and delivering bad customer service. MD Noor Iqbal&nbsp;wanted to address such issues, which was another reason for making Khati Shodai an online business.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67);\">&nbsp;</span></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67);\">Why Should use Khatishodai.com ?</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">khatishodai.com allows you to walk away from the daily needs of shopping and welcome an easy relaxed way of browsing and shopping..</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">No additionally stalling out in congested driving conditions, paying for parking, standing in long queues and carrying heavy bags – get everything you need, when you need, right at your doorstep. shopping online is now as easy as every product on your monthly shopping list is now available online at khatishodai.com</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">We are proud to have a big team of highly qualified members. Currently, the team consists of 50 staff. All are selected based on their unique skills required for the job. They are capable of doing bulk delivery service and managing multiple clients very easily and professionally.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">Bangladesh’s best online grocery store.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67);\">Our Target</strong></h3><ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">Customer Satisfaction</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">Save Valuable time</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">Reasonable Price</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">Provide Fresh Quality Food</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">Guaranteed Authentic Product</span></li></ul>');
